author: wn.com
title: GOP investigator says Republicans on Benghazi panel fired him over Clinton focus
text: A former investigator for the Republicans-led House Select Committee on Benghazi is alleging he was unlawfully fired from the panel for not focusing on Hillary Clinton and is vowing to file a federal complaint, according to The New York Times. ...
